<i>My name is Captain Saunders.</i>

04:35.135 --> 04:37.046
Commanding officer, Alpha Company.

04:37.255 --> 04:39.246
Third advance infantry
training brigade.

04:39.495 --> 04:41.486
Welcome to the infantry, gentlemen.

