01:20:05.735 --> 01:20:10.126
I know you're tired, but you'll be
doing a lot of this in the next year!

01:20:10.375 --> 01:20:11.728
If you're not...

01:20:11.935 --> 01:20:14.688
...then you're in a body bag.
- Where's Bozz?

01:20:14.895 --> 01:20:17.534
Waiting for a dust-off.

01:20:18.095 --> 01:20:20.529
Where is your squad leader?

01:20:20.935 --> 01:20:22.573
Is this his weapon?

01:20:22.815 --> 01:20:25.534
Does anybody know
where your squad leader is?

01:20:25.775 --> 01:20:27.128
Where is he, Johnson?

01:20:33.415 --> 01:20:36.691
- Where is your weapon, Private Bozz?
- Right here, sarge.

01:20:36.895 --> 01:20:38.089
I know that.

01:20:38.375 --> 01:20:41.845
The next time you decide
to take a piss or a fucking shit...

01:20:42.095 --> 01:20:44.131
...you make sure you have your weapon.

01:20:44.335 --> 01:20:47.532
Your weapon is your lifeline.
Why didn't you have it?

01:20:47.735 --> 01:20:51.171
I was gonna make a break for Mexico.
I didn't think I'd need it.

01:20:51.415 --> 01:20:52.768
Very funny.

01:20:53.575 --> 01:20:55.167
You take point.

01:20:55.695 --> 01:20:59.529
Paxton, take slack. Johnson, drag.
The rest of you fall in behind.

01:20:59.735 --> 01:21:00.929
Listen up.

01:21:01.175 --> 01:21:04.531
You'll square off
against the boys from yesterday.

01:21:04.775 --> 01:21:06.413
They may have booby traps.

01:21:06.815 --> 01:21:09.045
They may have forward observers
watching.

01:21:09.295 --> 01:21:12.367
They may do all manner of shit
that you don't know.

01:21:12.615 --> 01:21:17.325
That's why you will keep
your eyes open and your mouths shut.

01:21:17.695 --> 01:21:20.732
- Is that fucking understood?
- Yes, sarge.

01:21:22.655 --> 01:21:23.770
Let's move out.

01:21:26.375 --> 01:21:29.924
- Welcome back.
- You owe me 150 bucks.

01:21:34.175 --> 01:21:36.530
Hurry up, Paxton. Let's go.

01:22:04.335 --> 01:22:06.565
Dixie, dixie, my 12.

01:22:06.815 --> 01:22:08.214
Dixie, my 12.

01:22:51.215 --> 01:22:53.524
Move it! Come on!

01:23:42.495 --> 01:23:43.814
You okay?

01:24:45.695 --> 01:24:49.768
Fuck, Bozz. Joke's over.
Can't you see we're fucked?

01:24:50.015 --> 01:24:52.404
Relax. You'll be fine.

01:24:52.655 --> 01:24:54.327
You'll be fine.

01:25:29.375 --> 01:25:32.731
Wilson, what the hell are you doing?
That's live ammo.

01:26:26.895 --> 01:26:28.726
Ambush! 12:00!

01:26:35.135 --> 01:26:36.329
Live ammo!

01:26:39.215 --> 01:26:41.683
Cease fire! Cease fire!

01:27:03.175 --> 01:27:04.369
Private Wilson!

01:27:04.895 --> 01:27:06.692
Private-fucking-Wilson!

01:27:06.975 --> 01:27:09.409
Private Wilson, look at me, goddamn it!

01:27:09.775 --> 01:27:11.731
Oh, Jesus Christ!

01:27:13.815 --> 01:27:14.804
Look at me.

01:27:15.055 --> 01:27:17.205
You will place your weapon on safe!

01:27:17.615 --> 01:27:20.732
You will raise your weapon
above your fucking head...

01:27:20.975 --> 01:27:23.284
...or I'll blow
your fucking brains out!

01:27:24.935 --> 01:27:26.254
Oh, Jesus!

01:27:26.815 --> 01:27:28.134
Do it!

01:27:31.095 --> 01:27:32.847
On your fucking knees, now!

01:27:33.095 --> 01:27:34.608
Get on your fucking knees!

01:27:35.575 --> 01:27:39.090
You will be court-martialed!
Do you fucking hear me?

01:27:42.695 --> 01:27:44.765
- What happened?
- An accident. My fault.

01:27:46.215 --> 01:27:47.534
Let me look.

01:27:51.135 --> 01:27:52.534
Get him up.

01:28:04.895 --> 01:28:06.931
Let me see the eye.

01:29:10.815 --> 01:29:14.569
Let's go, move it!
This war is not gonna last forever!

01:29:14.815 --> 01:29:17.170
Bozz, bus number three!

01:29:17.415 --> 01:29:20.532
You don't want to miss this war!
Let's go!

01:29:23.975 --> 01:29:27.172
- Want to come along?
- I did, but you wouldn't let me.

01:29:28.215 --> 01:29:29.330
How's your eye?

01:29:30.935 --> 01:29:35.053
Got an injury bad enough to get out,
no permanent damage. Imagine that.

01:29:35.255 --> 01:29:37.007
More corny wisdom for your book.

01:29:37.255 --> 01:29:40.213
"In the country of the blind,
the one-eyed man is king."

01:29:40.815 --> 01:29:43.534
Pretty fancy shooting, Tex.
Thank you.

01:29:44.535 --> 01:29:47.652
It was just luck, Jim.
I could have killed you.

01:29:48.135 --> 01:29:49.727
No, it wasn't.

01:29:51.055 --> 01:29:53.091
Somebody had to take your place.

01:29:54.335 --> 01:29:56.849
Last chance.
Don't make me bring the war to you.

01:29:58.215 --> 01:29:59.887
Write me when you get there.

01:30:00.695 --> 01:30:02.367
This is it, man.

01:30:02.615 --> 01:30:04.606
No more phony Army buddy crap.

01:30:12.135 --> 01:30:13.727
Go home.

01:30:14.215 --> 01:30:16.126
Live a long time.

01:30:17.215 --> 01:30:19.331
Try not to be too much of an asshole.

01:30:20.975 --> 01:30:23.535
I'm gonna write
a whole book about this.

01:30:23.975 --> 01:30:25.567
Tell everyone about you.

01:30:29.375 --> 01:30:30.808
Sergeant Thomas...

01:30:31.055 --> 01:30:33.125
...sorry for my misbehavior earlier.

01:30:37.335 --> 01:30:38.529
Real sorry.

01:30:48.575 --> 01:30:50.452
See you back here. Take care.

01:30:50.655 --> 01:30:52.168
- Watch your back.
- See you.

01:30:52.415 --> 01:30:56.374
- I'll write a book about you, Bozz!
- No, you won't.

01:30:56.615 --> 01:30:59.129
Come on, quit playing.
That's my journal.

01:30:59.335 --> 01:31:01.769
Jesus! Bozz!

01:31:02.335 --> 01:31:04.929
Come on, quit fucking around.
That's my book!

01:31:06.175 --> 01:31:07.927
What are you doing? Shit!

01:31:08.175 --> 01:31:10.325
Stop the bus!

01:31:13.415 --> 01:31:15.167
What is this shit?

01:31:26.575 --> 01:31:28.531
<i>I never saw Bozz again.</i>

01:31:29.815 --> 01:31:32.204
<i>Some guys said he died in Nam...</i>

01:31:32.495 --> 01:31:34.326
<i>... but he was never listed.</i>

01:31:35.575 --> 01:31:38.135
<i>Some said he just</i>
<i>disappeared over there.</i>

01:31:38.495 --> 01:31:41.567
<i>One guy called and said</i>
<i>he thought he saw him in Mexico...</i>

01:31:41.815 --> 01:31:43.533
<i>... with a beautiful woman.</i>

01:31:44.895 --> 01:31:46.533
<i>But knowing Bozz...</i>

01:31:46.735 --> 01:31:49.932
<i>... he'd be pissed off</i>
<i>I was talking about him anyway.</i>

